track_notes: The second part of the trail is quite steep and the track visibility is sometimes close to non-existent. Pay attention on the way back!
track_title: EA7/MA-028 Gaucin Hacho de from Gaucin

track_notes: Thorn away. The beginning is good. Then it becomes difficult. Many thorns and partly the way is difficult to find. The mountain is beautiful with lots of space.
